profile:
Integrity Junk Removal  is handpicked as Top 3 Junk Removal service in Abbotsford. Integrity Junk Removal has had a 50-Point Inspection including everything from reputation, history, complaints, local reviews, nearness, satisfaction, trust and cost to the general excellence. Integrity Junk Removal is one of the Top!  You deserve only the best. 

Joel’s Background comes from 25 years of Direct Sales in wireless communications and the International Education, applying the principles of Dale Carnegie “How to win friends and influence people” in all daily transactions. After being in the corporate world of business for 25 years, Joel realized 3 things:

-He loves to meet new people
-He loves to help people
-He loves his community, Abbotsford, British Columbia
As a Father of four, Joel’s family needed him to be available for some of the Special Needs of his Children.

Joel and his family see Abbotsford Junk Removal as a means to do both, getting know families in their community while removing things that effect people’s daily lives in their home or businesses.

Joel sees Abbotsford Junk Removal as a way to reduce mental or marital stress, improving people’s living state, thus allowing them to take space back new projects, new businesses ultimately strengthening their family relationships.

profile:
WASTE DISPOSAL BINS AND RENTALS
Proudly serving the Lower Mainland, BC

Jobsite Bins serves these cities in the lower mainland of BC:

North Vancouver
West Vancouver
Vancouver
Burnaby
New Westminster
Richmond
Coquitlam
Port Coquitlam
Surrey
Langley
Abbotsford
We provide a responsive, cost effective and environmentally sound solution to your solid waste disposal and recycling needs.

We at Jobsite Bins, dump all of our construction loads at recycling depots where the materials are sorted and recycled.

Serving our community & devoted to maintaining the highest standards of care for our environment.

SERVICES
Our customers range from homeowners to commercial contractors. But no matter what your needs are, large or small, we have a variety of roll-off container sizes to meet any rubbish removal needs.

We have various containers in stock ranging in size from 10 cubic yards all the way up to 40 cubic yards. Our large selection of roll off container sizes means we have the right size container for every job.

Our roll off services are ideal for:

New Construction
Remodeling
Commercial & residential cleanups
Re-roofing
Yard waste removal
*Note : To better determine your bin size, a standard/regular pickup truck bed will hold 2 cubic yards of rubbish.

All our trucks are radio dispatched allowing us to better co-ordinate our pickup and drop off times. Also, we are able to handle emergency situations quickly and easily.
name: Jobsite Bins
